name: Stripped
description:
Inspired by Thai ghosts "Krasue", Who removes her head and entrails from the body and float away looking for rotten things to eat. 
In my work, I present the revelation of her sin such as lust, greed, selfishness.
The background is an upside down thai gravestone means a wandering ghost. (In the past, in Thailand, burials were more common than cremation).
